divs: Sighting DetailsIm so full of myself I might as well brag. Most important of all, I hate people, I hate every person Ive ever met. So anyhow I witness nightly UFO sighting for over 3 years. Hahahahaha, I have been denied work by every company, denied sex and dating by every woman although I am a handsome six foot four white man with blue eyes.
